        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWouldn't it be better to split PEMs from truststore/keystore creators etc.? I was thinking of a structure something like: abstract CertsCreator with abstract method createCertificates(List<String> keystoreData, List<String> truststoreData, PrivateKey pk) and concrete saveDataToLocation(). Then CertsCreator object could be composed in CertsCreatorFactory based on outputType.",
